    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it for all your upcoming adventures! It runs smoothly and looks great, making it a perfect pick if you want something reliable without breaking the bank. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to chat and show you around the car!",
      "price": 31500.0,
