    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This 2012 Porsche 911 Carrera is a stunning example of a modern classic, finished in a deep Basalt Black Metallic that still holds a high-gloss, mirror finish. The exterior is remarkably clean, showing only the light, honest peppering of stone chips on the front bumper consistent with spirited weekend drives. Inside, the Luxor Beige leather remains supple and fragrant; the cabin has been a smoke-free environment, and the dashboard is free of any sun-fading or cracks. While there is very minor softening on the driver's side entrance bolster, the interior presents beautifully overall. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the PCM navigation system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is dry and pulls with linear power, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recently completed major interval service. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident feedback. This is a turn-key, reliable enthusiast car that has been maintained with an open checkbook, offering a perfect balance of aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
